directories
============================

/app/views/layouts

  Where actual layouts live

/app/views/layouts/<sub directory>

  Where the partials used by the layouts live

html structure
=================================

%html
  %head
    %title
  %body
    %header#masthead
      %div#masthead_content
      %nav#global_nav
    %div#container
      %header#context_banner
        %div#banner_content
        %nav#banner_nav
      %div#local
        %div#column_left
          %nav#local_nav
        %div#column_center.with_left
          %article#content
      %footer#footer

there are some variations (context banner or not, left column or not, etc),
but this is the basic structure of every layout.
